                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18430130-635-offence-1 t18430130-name-367"></join>Mary Bowler</persName>: 1 hair-brush, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 night-gown, 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 pair of stock<lb></lb>ings, 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 1 pair of boots, 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18430130-name-368" type="victimName">
